title: ANCYL delegate gives birth on a bus - report
text:
Johannesburg - An ANC Youth League delegate from the Eastern Cape reportedly gave birth on a bus on Thursday morning.
She was travelling to Midrand, Gauteng, for the league's national elective conference, according to a report.
OR Tambo ANCYL secretary Mvuzo Mxenge reportedly confirmed the incident, but declined to provide further details, reported the Daily Dispatch .
He said the privacy of the new mother needed to be protected and that the delegates were close to Johannesburg.
